============================
How to configure product overview / browsing
============================

All your sellable items can be browsed on the Shop page of your website.


.. image:: ./media/shop.png
   :align: center

Most options are available in the ‘Customize’ menu.

.. image:: ./media/shop_customize.png
   :align: center

If you manage a B2B company, some options are tailored for you:
- List view & product description.
- Add to Cart (allows to populate a cart more quickly).

.. image:: ./media/shop_list.png
   :align: center

.. seealso::

  * :doc:`overview`
